         │
         ▼
Generate Report
         │
         ▼
Store Grade
         │
         ▼
Update Dashboard
A Better Idea Than CS50

Instead of forcing students to install Git locally, provide a browser-based IDE.

On2Code
│
├── Browser IDE
├── Terminal
├── Git Backend
├── Auto Save
├── Auto Grade
└── One-Click Submit

The student simply clicks:

Save
Run
Submit

while the platform performs:

git add .
git commit
git push